room_title: Escape room "Pele’s Stone Room" by Submerged Maui in Maui
room_description: Be a part of the elite amphibious assault team Maui Five-O. You will be boarding the assault submarine SS Wailea and taken deep into the Au-au channel that runs between the islands of Maui and Lanai. Your mission is to locate and retrieve Pele’s Stone, an ancient relic. Problem is, you're not the only ones after it. Do you have what it takes?
